  "texts": [
    "By investing in the appropriate infrastructure, optimizing edge computing solutions, and adopting scalable architectures, telecom operators can enhance their AI capabilities, ultimately improving network performance and user experience.",
    "The review highlights the effectiveness of AI techniques in anomaly detection within telecom environments.",
    "Specifically, deep learning methods such as CNNs and autoencoders have demonstrated superior accuracy and performance in identifying network anomalies.",
    "These advanced techniques excel at recognizing complex patterns in vast datasets, making them well-suited for the dynamic nature of telecommunications.",
    "However, traditional machine learning models, like SVMs and decision trees, continue to hold value, particularly in smaller-scale or less complex applications where their computational demands are more manageable."
